The paper deals with the segmentation of histopathological whole slide images using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning algorithms for image segmentation is also relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of traditional methods for comparison, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or deep learning (cs.DL).
